Package schoolmanagement.commonlib.model

Class Student

java.lang.Object
schoolmanagement.commonlib.model.User
schoolmanagement.commonlib.model.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Student extends User implements Serializable
Represents a student in the educational system, extending the User class and implementing Serializable. The Student class contains information such as first name, last name, birthdate, creation date, course enrollments, and course groups.
Author:
Djordje Ivanovic
